<h3>Neural Anaphora Resolution in Dialogue Revisited</h3>
Shengjie Li, Hideo Kobayashi and Vincent Ng.
<br>
<i>Proceedings of the CODI-CRAC 2022 Shared Task on Anaphora, Bridging, and Discourse Deixis in Dialogue</i>, <!-- pp. 16-31, --> 2022. 


<p>Click here for the 
