<p>
<h3>Abstract</h3>

We present the systems that we developed for all three tracks of the CODI-CRAC 2022 shared task, namely the anaphora resolution track, the bridging resolution track, and the discourse deixis resolution track. Combining an effective encoding of the input using the SpanBERT-Large encoder with an extensive hyperparameter search process, our systems achieved the highest scores in all phases of all three tracks.

